<HEAD>Warhol Exhibit Opens In Bratislava</HEAD>
<DATELINE>PRAGUE, Czechoslovakia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   An exhibit of works by the late
Andy Warhol, whose parents came from Slovakia, opened Wednesday in
the Slovak capital of Bratislava, the state news agency CTK
reported.
