discussing with Warhol's brother John, who is vice-president of the
Andy Warhol Foundation, the chances of opening a Warhol gallery in
Mikova, CTK said without elaboration.
   The news agency did not say how long the Bratislava exhibit will
show or whether it would go elsewhere in Czechoslovakia.
