Wednesday, up from $365.45 late Tuesday.
   In Zurich gold closed at a bid price of $365 a troy ounce, down
from $365.85 late Tuesday.
   Earlier, in Hong Kong, gold fell $1.40 to close at a bid $365.88.
   Silver was quoted at a bid price of $5.15 an ounce, down 1 cent
from Tuesday.
